SLRTimelapse v0.2

Tested, working fine.

Fearures Added:

Set amount of pictures to take.
Return to Main Screen when done.


SLRTimelapse v0.1

This needs some testing from my side, use it at your own risk!


Features for now:

Set time between pictures,
Hit run,
watch pictures counting up :)
 
To stop hit reset.


ToDo:
Calculate time left
