I used

+ Arduino Uno or clone
+ LCD 16x2 Keypad Shield
+ Camera with Remote Shutter option(Nikon D3100)
+ Maybe some properitary plug, i got myself something of for ebay for a few euro
+ PC817 Optocoupler


